# darknote premium (x402) config.
#
# by default everything runs on the mock facilitator, no env needed, no real
# money. that's what the tests and the offline demo use.

# --- optional: settle real USDC on Solana devnet instead of the mock ---
# flip both of these to 'devnet' (server + client), fund a devnet wallet with
# faucet USDC (https://faucet.circle.com, pick "Solana Devnet"), and connect
# that wallet on devnet.
#
# X402_MODE=devnet
# NEXT_PUBLIC_X402_MODE=devnet
# PREMIUM_PAYOUT_ADDRESS=<devnet address that should receive the USDC>
# X402_FACILITATOR_URL=<x402 devnet facilitator url>
# SOLANA_DEVNET_RPC=https://api.devnet.solana.com
# DEVNET_USDC_MINT=4zMMC9srt5Ri5X14GAgXhaHii3GnPAEERYPJgZJDncDU
